OL,3,CPolice urging canoe owner to call 999
OL,4,Cafter emergency response
OL,6,FEmergency services have been searching
OL,7,Fa stretch of the River Derwent near
OL,8,FWorkington after the discovery of an
OL,9,Funaccompanied canoe.
OL,11,FThey're urging the owner of the canoe
OL,12,Fto call 999 immediately.
OL,14,FPolice say they were called shortly
OL,15,Fbefore 8pm last night (23 July) and
OL,16,Fthat there were no reports of anyone
OL,17,Fmissing, or sightings of someone
OL,18,Fgetting into trouble.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/2
