OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1784913523
OL,3,CPolice urging canoe owner to call 999
OL,4,Cafter emergency response
OL,6,FCumbria Police said: "The canoe was
OL,7,Frecovered north-east of Workington
OL,8,FBridge.
OL,10,F"Given the presence of the
OL,11,Funaccompanied canoe, emergency
OL,12,Fservices are conducting searches in
OL,13,Fcase anyone has fallen in and got into
OL,14,Ftrouble.
OL,16,F"Cumbria Police would like to hear
OL,17,Ffrom anyone who believes the canoe may
OL,18,Fbelong to them ` or anyone who has any
OL,19,Fother information which may assist."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/2
